      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties derived from lot-specific tensile coupon testing (n=5 per lot); geometric inputs from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (E=114 GPa), yield strength (σ_y=880 MPa), and tangent modulus (E_t=1.8 GPa) derived from lot-specific tensile testing of Ti-6Al-4V rod and screw material. Specimen geometry inputs from CMM measurements (±0.01 mm). Vertebral block UHMWPE properties from supplier datasheet confirmed by three-point bend testing."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
